WEBVTT

00:00:29.666 --> 00:00:31.817
(Laughter)

00:00:31.841 --> 00:00:33.880
And the need to hug.

00:00:33.904 --> 00:00:35.396
Audience: Awww.

00:00:35.967 --> 00:00:40.023
But sloths are massively misunderstood.

00:00:40.047 --> 00:00:43.298
They've been saddled with a name
that speaks of sin

00:00:43.322 --> 00:00:46.514
and damned for their languorous lifestyle,

00:00:46.538 --> 00:00:50.117
which people seem to think
has no place amongst the fittest

00:00:50.141 --> 00:00:52.630
in the fast-paced race for survival.

00:00:53.268 --> 00:00:58.482
Well, I'm here to tell you
that we've got this animal all wrong --

00:00:58.506 --> 00:01:01.537
and how understanding
the truth about the sloth